    "text": [
        "Dear Sir,",
        "Good morning.",
        "I am writing this letter by requesting for offering an award to one of our community person, who helped poor people by started a charity called \"Help for Need\". He spent almost 50 percent of his salary for helping this cause. Also, he spread this charity information to other communities across our district to get more support.",
        "Charity started getting funds and distributed them to needed people in the form of food, clothes, Bedsheets and blankets. And, money spent to build a small 10-20 bed cottage for stay purpose.",
